		<div id="post_message_1253285">
                  <span id='devpost'>
                  Ok, we had a long discusion me and Avair today.<br />
Here are info.<br />
<br />
<b>Cold spells </b><br />
We'll get a progression with snare-root effect. Freeze and Icequake 4 will last longer than Freeze and Icequake 1.<br />
<br />
<b>Wards</b> <br />
We'll change the way they work so they can be more usefull in raid.<br />
<u>Nulling Ward</u>= Absorb 5% of incoming spell dmg and disperse a spell every 1min30s(group buff)<br />
<u>Mirror Ward</u>= Reflect a spell every 45sec (on 1 target only)<br />
<u>Chromatic Halo</u>= Absorb 10% of incoming spell dmg. (on 1 target only)<br />
<br />
<b>Opal Ring</b><br />
For those of you who played in beta 2-3, I don't know if you remember the buffs that had a random effect when we were hit. It's going to be, mainly, the same thing, but that will proc when we'll cast instead of when we are hit.<br />
Random effects are going to be something like:<br />
-Small mana regen<br />
-2k Rune<br />
-For 5seconds, spells you cast has 100% chance to do critical hit <br />
-Heal for 500<br />
-etc<br />
<br />
<b>Energy Shard</b><br />
We won't be able to conjure Energy Shard for other players (with +20% energy, 3 charge, 3min recast).<br />
But, we'll be able to trade our shard with other players.<br />
And, 1hour recast=15min recast<br />
<br />
<b>Forms</b><br />
<u>Asaya's Guile</u>: we'll fix detaunt proc<br />
<u>Seradon's Intensity</u>: With changes, this should put the sorc in more control of his damage. mana and allow us to start off with awesome dps.<br />
We'll get 2 abilities that can be used inside or outside of combat. One will increase rank by 1, and one will decrease rank by 1. We'll be able to cast it fast. Your rank will never go down. As long as you don't change it yourself.<br />
And, we'll probably completly remove the +energy cost. Instead of that, that will reduce our energy pool. Higher is your dmg, more your energy pool will be low. But spells will always cost the same.<br />
<br />
<b>Asaya Scorn</b><br />
We'll get it.<br />
<br />
<b>Anti-Magic Aura</b><br />
We'll get it. <br />
Instead of silence for 2sec after he casts, that will:<br />
lower their damage by a flat amount<br />
it would be a small flat amount, but it would be helpful. (more than the 2sec silence was)<br />
We'll keep the 1k dmg every time they cast a spell (in 15m range)<br />
<br />
I hope you'll enjoy.
                  </span>
		</div>
		<!-- / message -->
	
		
		
		
