		<div id="post_message_1253472">
                  
                  Ok, consider this.<br />
<br />
<br />
Lets say i have 8000 energy.<br />
<br />
and lets say i get an average idk... 400 energy / 6 seconds once all things are considered.<br />
<br />
400/8000= 5% of my energy regenerating every 6 seconds.<br />
<br />
Now lets say i use our dps form to max, and it lowers my energy by 50%.<br />
<br />
Now i only have 4000 energy, but the exact same regeneration rate, so now im getting 10% of my energy regenerating every 6 seconds<br />
<br />
My spells have not increased at all in cost.<br />
<br />
So, essentally if i dont go bellow 50% energy currently w/ normal raid buffed regeneration in no stance, then i wont ever run out of energy using your proposed change to the burn stance.<br />
<br />
